        <info>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 8.5pt;&quot;&gt;Ensure that you initiate contact with your lead within 24 hours: be fast or be last&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 8.5pt;&quot;&gt;Introduce yourself: tell the client who you are, where you received their details and convey the value you will bring to their life. Explain the process they can expect to follow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 8.5pt;&quot;&gt;Engage on next steps: ask the client if they are interested in proceeding and if they would like to schedule the first engagement. Send a follow up mail confirming your conversation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;TOP TIP: Unplanned calls in a busy day can cause frustration for a client. It may be a good idea to initiate contact through an email or WhatsApp and follow up with a call if you don’t hear back&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</info>
        <picklistValueName>Initiate 1st Contact</picklistValueName>
