    <pathAssistantSteps>
        <info>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 8.5pt;&quot;&gt;Congratulations, you have received a new lead! In order to convert this lead to a client, it is important that you nurture the lead and provide the person on the other side with a superior customer experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 8.5pt;&quot;&gt;Did you know that a response time of more than five minutes results in a 80% decline in the odds of qualifying your lead? Realistically, it is not always possible to respond in 5 minutes, but you shouldn’t let that discourage you. The research also says that businesses that act on leads within the first few hours are 60 times more likely to convert the lead. When it comes to new leads, think of it like this “be fast or be last”.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</info>
        <picklistValueName>New</picklistValueName>
    </pathAssistantSteps>
    <pathAssistantSteps>
